    "long_instructions": "#### Recreate a Song #1\r\n\r\nYour friend, Gemma, heard a great sound combination online. She took a recording of it and is asking you to recreate the sound. Using the coding blocks given to you, recreate the song for her. \r\n\r\nDo this: \r\n\r\n- Listen to the song in the media player. \r\n- Use the sounds given to you to build the song. \r\n- Look at the timeline below as reference.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/3899b4f06e1afcab08fa6080c0359192-image-1741387084637.37.44 PM.png)",
